reviewText: Fantastic Sci Fi package. Full of lots of action and interesting characters that add to the plot. If you like the typical Sci Fi shows on TV, you'll love these!
This Movie is very funny love it and it's a trip too Betty Wright is making the movie a great Movie a must see movie

I am a great fan of crocodile movie and i can say than Lake placid 1 is the best croc's movie. The second Lake Placid is a deception. Special effect of the first is the best but CGI image of the second is the one of the worst. A good deal to buy the two movie for collector like me!
